Dr. Jamilu Isyaku Gwamna, a Governorship hopeful in Gombe State has stated that workers are the most important drivers of positive change as he felicitates them on the 2022 workers day celebration. The front line PDP aspirant who said that the contributions of workers to the emergence and subsequent development of Gombe State can never be written off in the history of the state, pledged to bring good tidings to them by ensuring workers’ welfare and wellbeing is prioritised. A release made available to our correspondent in Gombe by Ibrahim Sani Shawai, Director of Publicity, Dr. Gwamna Campaign Organization, said Jamilu identified himself with the workers on this auspicious occasion. He said, “I greet all workers as well as solicit your supports in my ambition to govern the state”. “I pledge to bring good tidings to workers in Gombe State by ensuring workers’ welfare and wellbeing is prioritised,” Dr Gwamna added. Gwamna said ” I will ensure that there is a positive work environment for workers to better contribute their quotas to the state in a manner that will reflect positively on citizens across board.” Dr Gwamna therefore, greet all workers and wish them a happy 2022 Workers’ Day celebration.